<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentd23771c4915e400c878c14028efad2a6">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Rivers Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=117676"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Rivers Hospital is one of the leading <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Private hospitals in Hertfordshire">private hospitals in Hertfordhshire</a> with an excellent reputation for delivering high quality healthcare for self pay/insured and NHS patients. The hospital is located in Sawbridgeworth on the Essex.</p>
<p>The fully equipped ultra clean air theatre suite comprises four operating theatres all with laminar air flow. These are particularly suitable for <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatment/orthopaedics">Orthopaedic</a> surgery such as arthroscopy, <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/hip-surgery">hip replacements</a>, <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/knee-surgery/knee-replacements">knee replacements</a> and <a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/treatment/back-pain-and-spinal-care" target="_blank">spinal surgery</a>. A dedicated day surgery suite is suitable for minor surgery and <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatment/endoscopy">endoscopy</a>.</p>
<p>We have excellent levels of cleanliness and have effective infection control methods resulting in very low infection rates. All our facilities are regularly inspected and approved by the <a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/patients/cqc-regulation" target="_blank">Care Quality Commission</a>.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/patients/for-visitors" target="_blank">Free car parking</a> and disabled access is also available.</p>
<p>Our <a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/specialists" target="_blank">consultants</a> and nursing staff are highly experienced and have your care and comfort as their highest priority. During and after treatment, you will receive a standard of care which is second to none and all patients have the reassurance that theatre, paramedical services and a resident RMO is available 24 hours a day.</p>
<p>Rivers Hospital also provides private hospital treatments including full <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Diagnostic Services">diagnostic</a> and endoscopy procedures, orthopaedic surgery including <a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/treatments/hip-surgery" target="_blank">hip replacements</a>, <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/physiotherapy">Physiotherapy treatment </a>,  <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/cosmetic-surgery">cosmetic surgery</a>, <a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/treatments/cataract-surgery" target="_blank">cataract surgery</a> and <a href="https://www.rivershospital.co.uk/treatments/cancer-services" target="_blank">cancer services</a>.</p>
<p>We also offer <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/weight-loss-surgery">weight loss surgery</a> including: <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/weight-loss-surgery/gastric-banding">gastric bands</a> and <a href="http://www.rivers-hospital.co.uk/treatments/weight-loss-surgery/gastric-sleeve">gastric sleeve</a>.</p>
